    <h2>Home Page</h2>
    <p>Welcome to the Leaf Me Alone company data management system. This platform can help you update your customer records, orders, 
        plant stock, and suppliers. See below for a quick overview of what actions you can perform for each record.</p>
    <h3>Customers</h3>
    <p>Within the <a href="customers">"Customers"</a> page, you are able to view the current customers of Leaf Me Alone. You will also be able to add new customers, edit customer information and delete customer records.</p>
    <h3>Orders</h3>
    <p>The <a href="orders">"Orders"</a> page allows you to view all the orders for Leaf Me Alone. You can add new orders, update existing orders, and delete orders.</p>
    <h3>Plants</h3>
    <p>The <a href="plants">"Plants"</a> page provides an inventory of plants Leaf Me Alone currently sells. View this page to update the inventory or make adjustments, add new plants to the inventory, or delete a plant from our stock.</p>
    <h3>Suppliers</h3>
    <p>Next, our <a href="suppliers">"Suppliers"</a> page gives you a view of all of our plant suppliers. Navigate to this page to update, add, or delete suppliers for our plants.</p>
    <h3>Plants Suppliers</h3>
    <p>Finally, the <a href="plantssuppliers">"Plants Suppliers</a> page allows you to see which plants are supplied by a provider.</p>